t%2Flarge-banner.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Flarge-banner.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Flarge-banner.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Flarge-banner.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4"/></div><div class="work-case-body"><aside class="work-case-sidebar" aria-label="Project details"><p class="work-case-eyebrow">Sift</p><dl class="work-case-meta"><div class="work-case-meta-row"><dt>Timeline</dt><dd>Concept</dd></div><div class="work-case-meta-row"><dt id="work-case-categories-sift">Categories</dt><dd><ul class="work-case-category-list" aria-labelledby="work-case-categories-sift"><li>Concept</li><li>Product Design</li><li>Web Design</li><li>HR Tech</li><li>AI</li></ul></dd></div><div class="work-case-meta-row"><dt>Location</dt><dd>Concept · Spec Work</dd></div><div class="work-case-meta-row"><dt>Year</dt><dd>2026</dd></div></dl></aside><div class="work-case-main"><div class="work-case-intro"><h1 class="work-case-title" id="work-case-title"><span class="TextReveal-module-scss-module__WSa0mG__line" data-text-reveal-line="true"><span class="TextReveal-module-scss-module__WSa0mG__inner" data-text-reveal-inner="true" style="filter:blur(14px);opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px)">Hire for what they can do,</span></span><span class="TextReveal-module-scss-module__WSa0mG__line" data-text-reveal-line="true"><span class="TextReveal-module-scss-module__WSa0mG__inner" data-text-reveal-inner="true" style="filter:blur(14px);opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px)">not how they write a CV</span></span></h1><p class="work-case-lede">Sift is a concept for an AI hiring platform — designed to explore what candidate screening looks like when the AI does the reading and the hiring manager does the deciding. We took the product from name and positioning through web presence and product design: a complete vision for a tool that ranks every applicant by fit, explains the reasoning behind each score, and lets founders focus on interviews, not inboxes.</p></div><div class="work-case-sections"><section class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__section" aria-labelledby="_R_qislubsnlnb_" aria-describedby="_R_qislubsnlnbH1_"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__inner"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__intro"><h2 id="_R_qislubsnlnb_" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__title">Brief</h2><p id="_R_qislubsnlnbH1_" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__subtitle">Hire on signal, not on luck</p><p class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__paragraph">Most hiring processes rely on a founder speed-reading a stack of CVs and pattern-matching against a rough mental model of what &quot;good&quot; looks like. Sift was designed to formalise that signal: the AI reads every application against the role requirements and returns a ranked list with scores and reasoning, so the decision-maker starts from a shortlist, not a pile. We designed the name, positioning, web presence, and product screens to tell that story end to end.</p></div></div></section><section class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__section" aria-labelledby="_R_1aislubsnlnb_" aria-describedby="_R_1aislubsnlnbH1_"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__inner"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__intro"><h2 id="_R_1aislubsnlnb_" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__title">Positioning</h2><p id="_R_1aislubsnlnbH1_" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__subtitle">&quot;200 applicants. 3 worth your time. We&#x27;ll find them.&quot;</p><p class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__paragraph">The headline is deliberately specific — the number makes it real. Every founder who has posted a role and opened their inbox the next morning knows what 200 applicants feels like. Sift&#x27;s web design leans warm and light, a deliberate contrast with the dark-mode SaaS aesthetic: this product is about people, not pipelines, and the visual tone reflects that. The hero shows three candidate cards with AI match scores visible from the first scroll.</p></div><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__figureWrap"><figure class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__figure"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__imageFrame"><img alt="Sift — hero section with candidate cards and AI match scores" loading="lazy" width="1600" height="900" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__image" style="color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 100vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=384&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4"/></div></figure></div></div></section><section class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__section" aria-labelledby="_R_1qislubsnlnb_" aria-describedby="_R_1qislubsnlnbH1_"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__inner"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__intro"><h2 id="_R_1qislubsnlnb_" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__title">Candidate pipeline</h2><p id="_R_1qislubsnlnbH1_" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__subtitle">Every applicant scored, ranked, and explained</p><p class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__paragraph">The main dashboard is a ranked candidate list per role, sorted by AI match score descending. Each row shows the candidate&#x27;s current role, their score as a colour-coded progress bar, their pipeline stage, and a one-line AI summary of fit. Switching between open roles at the top of the screen updates the list instantly. The AI score is the most visually dominant element on the page — because it is the product.</p></div><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__figureWrap"><figure class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__figure"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__imageFrame"><img alt="Sift — candidate pipeline dashboard with AI match scores" loading="lazy" width="1600" height="900" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__image" style="color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 100vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-roles.webp&amp;w=384&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-roles.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-roles.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-roles.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-roles.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-roles.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-roles.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-roles.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-roles.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-roles.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4"/></div></figure></div></div></section><section class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__section" aria-labelledby="_R_2aislubsnlnb_" aria-describedby="_R_2aislubsnlnbH1_"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__inner"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__intro"><h2 id="_R_2aislubsnlnb_" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__title">Candidate intelligence</h2><p id="_R_2aislubsnlnbH1_" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__subtitle">Score, reasoning, and a clear next action</p><p class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__paragraph">Clicking any candidate opens a right-side panel with the full AI assessment: a match score out of 100, a skills breakdown showing exact matches and gaps against the role, and a plain-English explanation of why the score is what it is. Work history sits below for context. The panel closes with three actions — schedule an interview, pass, or save for later — so the hiring decision requires one click, not a discussion.</p></div><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__figureWrap"><figure class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__figure"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__imageFrame"><img alt="Sift — candidate detail panel with AI assessment and skills breakdown" loading="lazy" width="1600" height="900" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__image" style="color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 100vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-candidate-drawer.webp&amp;w=384&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-candidate-drawer.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-candidate-drawer.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-candidate-drawer.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-candidate-drawer.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-candidate-drawer.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-candidate-drawer.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-candidate-drawer.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-candidate-drawer.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fsift%2Fdashboard-candidate-drawer.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4"/></div></figure></div></div></section></div></div></div></header><div class="work-case-footer-cta"><div class="Grid-module-scss-module__OPYCKW__grid work-cards work-